{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_52_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 北海道グルメで完全復活",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、それぞれ旅行を楽しんでくれているみたいだな\n俺はゆっくり昼ご飯でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems everyone is enjoying their trip\nI'll have a leisurely lunch…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん……？　ロビーに誰か倒れてる！？\nあれは……さくらか！？　一体どうしたんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…? Someone's collapsed in the lobby!?\nIs that… Sakura!? What happened!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7726.3492711,
          "startTime": 18.7930159378
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16026.349271100004,
          "startTime": 27.0930159378
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？　う、うう……\nジン、ギスカン……とん……かつ……ザン……ギ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…? Uh‚ ugh…\nJingi… sukan… Pork… Cutlet… Zan… gi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1296826045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.5630159378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おい、しっかりしろ、さくら！　よく聞こえないぞ\n一体どうしたんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ pull yourself together‚ Sakura! I can't hear it\nWhat's going on!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.6212471962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "とんかつを……とんかつを、食べさせて下さい……\nジンギスカンでも……いいです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pork cutlet… please let me eat pork cutlet…\nJingisukan would be fine… too…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2545805295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.2045805295
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.2045805295
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "川咲さくら、北海道グルメで完全復活！\nとっても美味でしたー！　わっしょい、わっしょい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura Kawasaki‚ makes a complete recovery with Hokkaido gourmet food!\nIt was so deliciousー! Wasshoi‚ wasshoi",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6212471962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.6212471962
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.0879138629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは良かったよ……まさかお腹が空いて\n倒れているなんて思わなかったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's sounds good… I never thought\nyou'd collapse from hunger…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 67.3195011775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、恥ずかしながら……でも、これには\nふかーい訳があるんです！　実は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ it's a bit embarrassing… but there's a\nvery deep reason for this! Actually…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4195011775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――北海道旅行　一週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One week before the Hokkaido trip",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.419503212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4861698787
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4861698787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、北海道旅行楽しみだなぁ\n何食べようかなぁ……あ、そうだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay‚ I'm so excited for the Hokkaido trip!\nWhat should I eat… Oh‚ that's it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5861698787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1194960912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "今からお坊さんみたいな生活をしたら北海道のグルメを\n最高に楽しめるんじゃないかな！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I live like a monk from now on‚ I'll be able to enjoy\nHokkaido's gourmet food to the fullest!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3861698787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4194899877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "だってダイエットしてる時のとんかつが\n一番美味しく感じるもん！　きっとそうだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because pork cutlet tastes the best\nwhen you're on a diet! I'm sure that's it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6528304418,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11940.004068999997,
          "startTime": 112.5928345108
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まれば忙しくなるぞー善は急げだよね\n早速みんなに伝えてこよ～っと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that I've decided‚ I'm going to be busyー‚ strike while the iron is hot\nI'll go tell everyone right away~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5528284073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 114.6028233212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　今日のご飯はとんかつ部位違いの二枚！？\nわーい！　盆と正月が一緒にきた気分だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Today's meal is two tonkatsu cuts from different parts!?\nYayー! It feels like Obon and New Year's have come at the same timeー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.619495074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "え……我慢しないのかって？　ひっ……わ、忘れてた\n北海道グルメを楽しむために修行僧になるんだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… don't you hold back? Eek… I-I forgot\nI was supposed to become training monk to enjoy Hokkaido's gourmet food…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7528284073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 143.0694899878
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 143.0694899878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって日々キャベツを食べながらとんかつを\n眺めるつらーい毎日を過ごしていたんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how I spent my days‚ eating cabbage\nand staring at pork cutlet… It was such a painful time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9528284073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに北海道旅行を\n楽しみにしてくれていたとは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I didn't realize you were looking forward to\nHokkaido trip so much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.3569502514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんな生活も今日で終わり……とんかつに\nジンギスカン、ザンギ、パフェに会える……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ that life ends today… I'll get to see\npork cutlet‚ jingisukan‚ zangi‚ and parfait…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.9902886708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 166.4902835847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "そう思って旅館を出ようとしたら、なんと……！\nお財布を寮に忘れて来たことに気付いたんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking that‚ I stepped out of the inn‚ and I realized…!\nI'd forgotten my wallet at the dorm!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.8902886708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "誰かに借りようと思ったんですけどみんな観光に\n出ちゃってて……それからは記憶がありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried to borrow one from someone‚ but everyone was out\nsightseeing… I don't remember anything after that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1902886708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 185.723616918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……空腹と財布を忘れたショックで\nあんな所で倒れてたのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… you collapsed there because of\nhunger and shock of forgetting your wallet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.3564218692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
