      "text": "北海道産のメロンをたっくさん使ったパフェに\n特大生キャラメルパフェ！　さぁ一緒に食べましょー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A parfait made with lots of Hokkaido melons\nand extra-large caramel parfait! Come on‚ let's eat togetherー!",
        "id": ""
